    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in good shape and represents a solid, reliable choice for a used car buyer seeking quality without the premium of a mint-condition vehicle. The car shows only minor signs of wear consistent with normal use, including light surface scratches and modest interior wear, but nothing that affects its performance or reliability. Mechanically, the vehicle runs well and has been maintained with care. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and electronics \u2014 are functioning properly. This is a dependable daily driver that offers real value for buyers who want a step above a basic used car without stretching their budget to the top of the market.",
