    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Practical, Affordable & Ready for Daily Use \u2014 A Budget-Friendly Option for Practical Drivers! This used car is in fair condition and gets the job done for everyday transportation needs. The exterior shows noticeable wear consistent with its age and use, and the interior has seen its share of miles \u2014 but it remains functional and road-ready. Mechanically, it runs reliably for routine driving, making it a sensible choice for buyers who need dependable transportation without breaking the bank. If you're looking for straightforward value at an honest price, this one deserves a look!",
