    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Budget-Friendly Fixer or Parts Car \u2014 Priced to Move!** Looking for an affordable project or a temporary ride? This vehicle could be just what you need! This car is in poor condition \u2014 it has visible wear, mechanical issues that will need attention, and cosmetic damage, so it's best suited for someone handy or looking for a parts vehicle. That said, it's priced accordingly so you know exactly what you're getting \u2014 no surprises! If you're a DIY enthusiast or just need something ultra-affordable to get around, this could be a great opportunity. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you! \ud83d\udd27",
      "price": 6500.0,
