      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 a rare find on the used car market that will impress even the most discerning buyers. The exterior is virtually flawless, with deep, lustrous paint showing no signs of chips, scratches, or fading, and all body panels are perfectly aligned with no evidence of prior collision or bodywork. The interior is equally immaculate, with seats, carpets, and trim all presenting as near-new, free from stains, wear, or odors. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs with smooth, confident power, and all mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and electronics \u2014 are functioning exactly as they should. Service records are available and reflect consistent, attentive maintenance throughout the vehicle's life. This is a turn-key car that requires absolutely nothing \u2014 simply drive it home and enjoy it from day one.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $47,000, a price that honestly reflects its exceptional mint condition \u2014 and we mean that sincerely. The exterior is virtually flawless: the paint retains a deep, showroom-quality shine with no visible scratches, chips, or blemishes. Body panels are perfectly aligned, trim pieces are intact and pristine, and the glass is crystal clear without any chips or cracks. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot \u2014 seats show no wear, the dashboard and door panels are unmarked, and all controls and electronics function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and performs with full power and responsiveness. All mechanical systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, and cooling \u2014 are in top working order. Service records are complete and up to date. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that truly needs nothing. What you see is what you get: a meticulously cared-for car in the best condition you'll find on the market.",
      "price": 47000.0,
